rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Running a shop here, you get to hear
all sorts of interesting stories.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's right in front of the
port, so there are a lot of
adventurers and merchants.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
For example, it seems each
Divine Beast has several
places called Secret Areas.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
In Gula, there's a place called
Dawnview Grotto where you can
see a magnificent view.

rows.label: tlk41300021_01_msg0005
rows.name:
For an adventurer, going to various
places and finding wonderful scenery
must be one of the joys, don't you think?
